# Lumi Flutter UI rules

**Do not duplicate policy here.** Before editing `lib/**/*.dart`, read **`CLAUDE.md`** at the repository root (covers `DESIGN.md`, spacing/radii/type tokens, `LumiColors`, Theme — no hardcoded UI colors).

After substantive UI edits, run `flutter analyze` (and tests if behavior changed).
